y.gif&h=f8565989&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n召喚報警撚"},{"pid":"d37ebf2af28f02bdb1e73dcc2ac9f09db3382300","tid":379324,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T09:24:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>收都唔好收check啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n收cash最實際</blockquote><br />\n要比人捉痛腳一樣捉到姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80daa982d01ed39027046cad20f9398b37a642f9","tid":379324,"uid":1915,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T09:28:21.000Z","msg":"完成左先收架喎<br />\n咁計夕山賣仔收貼士係咪都犯法"},{"pid":"b7ff30d4bddb2b3c9c54a83fcef9ae16c31531b4","tid":379324,"uid":1915,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T09:28:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>完成左先收架喎<br />\n咁計外賣仔收貼士係咪都犯法</blockquote>"},{"pid":"d658d0ddd03e5e519f02aa01bcd3cf1278a1b1c2","tid":379324,"uid":82175,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T09:28:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>叫佢地請食飯算啦，金額不限，只要唔外賣拎走就唔會犯法。</blockquote><br />\n請跳茶舞得唔得？</blockquote><br />\n當場享用的款待唔算賄賂 <br />\n<br />\n來源：廉政行動2014"},{"pid":"9c76afc5cb5bc8772229d9c72de0da7dea730a25","tid":379324,"uid":54502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T09:32:43.000Z","msg":"多數話請食流浮山海鮮，不過講十次都冇去一次"},{"pid":"0f3a37df923e8a5e8ec084251dc4ad534a95f44e","tid":379324,"uid":132076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T09:33:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>完成左先收架喎<br />\n咁計夕山賣仔收貼士係咪都犯法</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n代理人（通常為僱員）在未得主事人（通常為僱主）的許可下，不得因辦理其主事人的事務或業務而索取或接受利益；而提供利益者亦同樣有罪。<br />\n<br />\n雇主比你收就得，唔比，就唔得。"},{"pid":"d09f8dd1c0a36dbbfc40709a4f60ba25977d9b1c","tid":379324,"uid":132076,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T09:37:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>今日幫公司傾成左單job..唔係話好單，不過對個supplier 黎講，應該幫左佢公司唔少忙。<br />\n搞掂單野臨走時，對方代表竟然拉埋我一二邊猛咁講多謝，仲表示想比啲禮物我（一張現金check, 銀碼大約5位數咁試上下）。<br />\n我最後無要到就走左。<br />\n比著你地，會唔會受？有無試過咁嘅情況？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n請參考防止賄賂條例第九條。簡單黎講，你老闆之前話比你收，就可以收，無講過，最好唔好收。收左要即刻返去禀報比老闆知，由佢定奪。"},{"pid":"58c70e713178c33778e4eee32480eb6a1c12882e","tid":379324,"uid":28001,"like":6,"dislike":3,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T09:52:55.000Z","msg":"成日都有。不過一次都無收過<br />\n一千幾百, 幾十萬, 10%回佣乜鳩都有人嚟過<br />\n<br />\n最誇張一次係去開完會走嘅時候<br />\n門口保安比個紙箱我話我漏底咗<br />\n我話唔係我嘅，佢話係老細比我嘅<br />\n我一打開全部都係錢嚟。不過我無收<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99609174885611cd2378dbda589a3e5a61fa5f36","tid":379324,"uid":9566,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T09:54:10.000Z","msg":"做工程 多撚到你唔信"},{"pid":"51df1372b976944453e76b171e6a42ce1b0de3da","tid":379324,"uid":28001,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T09:55:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>做工程 多撚到你唔信</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n工程一定多到仆街"},{"pid":"86ba376f003f1c1d4ca1192500f72220d919506d","tid":379324,"uid":12628,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T09:56:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>做工程 多撚到你唔信</blockquote><br />\n係，不過工程好多時係公司間有默契嘅嘅回佣。公司比你收先得，如果唔係，一樣死得"},{"pid":"bd596b82ce22cac26b0ea22615cf0ffd3af16801","tid":379324,"uid":112583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T09:57:22.000Z","msg":"做工廠既成日發生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3a736f84f81b356eb06090261a036f8fd89b26b","tid":379324,"uid":44486,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T10:00:22.000Z","msg":"唔好用香港自己名既戶口<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/42.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4287330c5870c0d1993b57d8a7157c7a29573d57","tid":379324,"uid":12628,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T10:01:09.000Z","msg":"大陸係合理化晒賄絡手段，香港真係唔可以行回頭路。老實，如果張check係一百萬，都唔可以收。收到分分鐘嘔凸"},{"pid":"898d87f087f47f49b9b8484f5291b80c1a55bfb4","tid":379324,"uid":120935,"like":1,"dislike":0,"sc