hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n收左我仲笨實呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8382d6f46e7564ee1fa64650c2178c23979f9ab7","tid":379324,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T11:31:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a85a78aed8effd8358968994ec0e813b63b7b90","tid":379324,"uid":13910,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T11:37:42.000Z","msg":"試過去踢耶撚個d足球賽事<br />\n開波前一個中<br />\n對面領隊塞左$2k比我地<br />\n叫我地要輸夠5粒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1ebbe69bdafafc29984b07ee2b6c65609205eef","tid":379324,"uid":7673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T11:46:26.000Z","msg":"發夢試過比回佣人"},{"pid":"ac09748c2cb3d46737837f16bfbe795aa8a9ec16","tid":379324,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T12:01:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>試過去踢耶撚個d足球賽事<br />\n開波前一個中<br />\n對面領隊塞左$2k比我地<br />\n叫我地要輸夠5粒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n最後咩比數？"},{"pid":"51499472eaaf574af9d26627283e6bfb9053ae0a","tid":379324,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T12:19:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2cd4654f00a3a358da74e15667118d7b8b8e17df","tid":379324,"uid":133776,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T12:28:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>試過去踢耶撚個d足球賽事<br />\n開波前一個中<br />\n對面領隊塞左$2k比我地<br />\n叫我地要輸夠5粒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n最後咩比數？</blockquote><br />\n4:2<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc3868214d4c8a71231504701b59694190c8ad23","tid":379324,"uid":125255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T12:31:52.000Z","msg":"如果a比錢叫b做一樣野<br />\n但其實b係無份干預件事<br />